---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 473
  - Title: Gospel of Thomas
    Logion: 10,11
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Subversion-The Wrathful Side=The Last Times
---
Jesus said： I have cast fire upon the world, and see, I guard it until
it (the world) is afire.

Jesus said： This heaven shall pass away and the one above it shall
pass away.
